{"id":"summaries/2026-01-07-call-with-emily-stevens","title":"Call with Emily Stevens","type":"summaries","html":"<p>January 2026 Apple Note from <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/yahir-gonzalez\">Yahir</a> containing only a <code>com.apple.m4a-audio</code> placeholder — a phone-call recording with <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/emily-stevens\">Emily Stevens</a> that didn't re-import as audio. Body has no text. Sits in the <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/emily-stevens\">Emily</a> thread arc that ends in the <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2026-04-27-e-51st-st\">2026 04 27 e 51st st</a> post-mortem voice-memo.</p>\n<p><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/yahir-gonzalez\">yahir gonzalez</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/emily-stevens\">emily stevens</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2026-04-27-e-51st-st\">2026 04 27 e 51st st</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/austin-tx\">austin tx</a></p>\n","related":[{"id":"entities/austin-tx","label":"Austin, Texas"},{"id":"summaries/2025-12-19-call-with-nonas","label":"Call with Nonas"},{"id":"summaries/2026-04-27-e-51st-st","label":"E 51st St — Apr 27 2026 Emily-relationship post-mortem"},{"id":"entities/emily-stevens","label":"Emily Stevens"},{"id":"entities/yahir-gonzalez","label":"Yahir Gonzalez"}]}
